Posts.Content: Hey! I am so glad everything went well for you! I done very well with all of my treatments-I was alittle sick at my stomach the day of & day after,(but not bad) & alittle tired. I had it on Wed. & by Sunday I was completely back to normal. I think alot of mine was mental- the closer I got to tx center the sicker I got with NO meds!!! Just keep positive & determined!!!!! Aimee
Posts.Title: WOW FIRST TREATMENT OVER
